snippet.title: Observation at Freddy's Night 5 (51% remaining)
snippet.description:
Version 1.4.9 of Observation at Freddy's. Mostly just using camera instead of door for freddy, timing the door slam to be right before animatronics would attack, and opening the door as soon as the animatronic has left. 

Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/observation-at-freddys/921907
